# Library API

API quản lý sách đơn giản sử dụng Flask.

# Group Books

## Books Collection [/books]

### Get all books [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
          {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "Book A",
            "author": "Author A"
          }
        ]


### Create a new book [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "title": "New Book",
          "author": "New Author"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 1,
          "title": "New Book",
          "author": "New Author"
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

        {
          "message": "Missing required fields: title, author"
        }


## Book Detail [/books/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 1 (number, required) - ID của sách

### Get book by ID [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 1,
          "title": "Book A",
          "author": "Author A"
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
          "message": "Book not found"
        }


### Update book [PUT]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "title": "Updated Book",
          "author": "Updated Author"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 1,
          "title": "Updated Book",
          "author": "Updated Author"
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

        {
          "message": "Missing required fields: title, author"
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
          "message": "Book not found"
        }


### Delete book [DELETE]

+ Response 204

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
          "message": "Book not found"
        }